maintainers.name: Cohen Carlisle
maintainers.bio: I love Elixir for its productivity, elegant syntax, and functional nature. I've written it professionally and for fun. I hope to help people get excited about Elixir and learn some things myself, as well.

maintainers.name: Tim Austin
maintainers.bio: Exercism has been a great way for me to stay current and expand my developer experience in new areas.  I am excited to be working with the elixir track, because I appreciate the clarity/idiomaticity of the elixir language.  I want others to enjoy this track as much as I have.

maintainers.name: Oleksii Filonenko
maintainers.bio: Elixir is a passion of mine, being functional, elegant and productive. After being a mentor for some time, I decided to be a maintainer. Looking forward to it!

maintainers.name: Everett Griffiths
maintainers.bio: Elixir developer based in Los Angeles, former instructor at USC

maintainers.name: Angelika Tyborska
maintainers.bio: Working with Elixir since 2017. I love it for its elegant syntax, great performance, pattern matching, and immutability.
